Text: few pictures are bad but most are awesome. definitely worth download

really not that impressed with this collection. more than half are low rez and 1/3 are very poor in composition. stop signs do not belong in landscape pics, nor do cars and people, and strip mines and power lines? come on. i ended up  with about 35 keepers that were desktop worthy. thanks though.
